{"tid":2159250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：誰不屬於自己的祖國，那麼他也就不屬於人類。","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:55:59.000Z","uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e5443da5b76b3123e19bc6593826eeecc83b39ed","tid":2159250,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;世紀大漢奸！&rdquo;在黎智英被香港警方押解到西貢遊艇會調查取證時，現場有香港市民大聲怒斥。黎智英被保釋後，仍有不少市民在其家門前高舉標語&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;禍港漢奸沒有好下場&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英被捕之後，市民無不拍手叫好，然而弔詭的是，身在大洋彼岸的美國副總統、國務卿、國家安全顧問等一眾美國高官，作出了超乎尋常的激烈反應。這其實也不難理解，自己的&ldquo;傀儡&rdquo;被繩之以法，作為幕後主子的&ldquo;洋大人&rdquo;哪裡能坐得住，肯定要放放狠話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/3qGBpicMFJ42v08ygBh9MRkLNmMg6QGXicwDgNNfSibzBSB751n6DYynJkyOf4ib0FRLspefDzmV5dumJuricDtJhibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3qGBpicMFJ42v08ygBh9MRkLNmMg6QGXicwDgNNfSibzBSB751n6DYynJkyOf4ib0FRLspefDzmV5dumJuricDtJhibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=3234c93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，一些外國和境外勢力一直沒有放棄干預香港事務。香港回歸祖國懷抱之後，西方一些政客仍然沉醉於殖民時代的春秋大夢，妄圖繼續操控香港，為此不惜撕破面具、赤膊上陣，在政治上扶持代理人，在經費上資助亂港組織。<br />\n<br />\n賣國是條不歸路，偏偏香港就有極少數人以崇洋媚外為榮光，以出賣香港為己任。聽說&ldquo;英國主子&rdquo;拋出&ldquo;BNO&rdquo;護照誘餌，有人欣喜若狂；得知&ldquo;美國大人&rdquo;制裁香港，有人高呼&ldquo;感謝施恩&rdquo;；遊說西方反華勢力干預，恨不能將香港雙手奉上。口口聲聲愛香港、為香港，實際上卻是害香港、賣香港。這種令人作嘔的賣國行徑、漢奸心態，良知何在？道義何在？分明是香港的恥辱、中國人的敗類！<br />\n<br />\n從黎智英這樣的&ldquo;老奸巨猾&rdquo;，到黃之鋒、羅冠聰、周庭之流的&ldquo;黃口小兒&rdquo;，難道他們不知道自己的滿貫惡行家國難容？只是厚顏無恥而已。黎智英獲保釋後在海外社交媒體上迅速開了一場直播，流下假惺惺的淚水，恬不知恥地聲稱：&ldquo;香港對我實在太好，我必須給這個地方一個交代，這是我的家園，讓我能擁有一切的家園。&rdquo;事實上，他此前曾聲稱，樂見香港成為&ldquo;大象相爭下遭殃的草地&rdquo;。可見他不僅要在經濟上收割財富，還要在政治上謀求私利，為此縱然出賣香港、出賣靈魂，他也在所不惜。<br />\n<br />\n隨著香港國安法的頒布實施，像黎智英這種外部勢力的政治代理人已窮途末路。出賣自己祖國的人，在哪裡都會被人們唾棄。他們以為，有了外國主子撐腰打氣就能在香港為所欲為？他們以為，惺惺作態就能蒙蔽廣大香港市民？顯然，他們錯判了形勢，嚴重低估了中央政府和香港特區政府、香港市民維護國家主權和安全的決心。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;誰不屬於自己的祖國，那麼他也就不屬於人類。&rdquo;為禍香港的漢奸國賊們，不妨暗地裡品品這個道理，想想自己無可逃避的悲慘結局。"},{"pid":"52020d89d34803ba8ad848dcd15b77f5759004de","tid":2159250,"uid":79562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"工人無祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22a4467e4968aea5dec65f0cce00fa0b39c3c61","tid":2159250,"uid":58841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"如何理解《共產黨宣言》中&ldquo;工人沒有祖國&rdquo;的論述"},{"pid":"65cffa2c88b11790af0e492bd048eebe0aad5b07","tid":2159250,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Grothendieck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAlexander_Grothendieck&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=d9d43ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Grothendieck</a><br />\n<br />\n終於明白點解佢可以咁勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1130cbc9f7c21eba28a42d38f87e1f3a4f67f3a","tid":2159250,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"52020d89d34803ba8ad848dcd15b77f5759004de","tid":2159250,"uid":79562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"工人無祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"工人不是人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84239c4fd8ce619265f8ef33801149c6242e94","tid":2159250,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"食屎啦咁乜嘢祖國 點解你咁多人喺澳洲加拿大美國甚至乎歐洲"},{"pid":"d7dc99a5d4a268104fe890f6646f82b59337db7b","tid":2159250,"uid":353256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"我祖國係香港  <br />\n完"},{"pid":"b200f43c425bbcea203ef4203d2dfdd64aa001cd","tid":2159250,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e84239c4fd8ce619265f8ef33801149c6242e94","tid":2159250,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"食屎啦咁乜嘢祖國 點解你咁多人喺澳洲加拿大美國甚至乎歐洲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:12:23.000Z","msg":"所以過到去咪做小粉紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058df48d949e7c84e9cd04037b85dfeb008842c9","tid":2159250,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Xk35zb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Xk35zb.jpg&h=0b4b467c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b14e1d558168eeef5623ca7b89f3121211933c39","tid":2159250,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8u7fFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8u7fFx.jpg&h=4dfb21d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n滅完人國根住話人背叛<br />\n都算係賤格之最"},{"pid":"fc8101044f6251fadc2c0e77eeed712e8e409d93","tid":2159250,"uid":273218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52020d89d34803ba8ad848dcd15b77f5759004de","tid":2159250,"uid":79562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"工人無祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MX47fFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMX47fFV.jpg&h=04327071&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n滅完人國再話人背叛<br />\n佢地都算係無恥之最"},{"pid":"821893ed5dfcae02c073c6a0b0aa1fd5f9a57a6f","tid":2159250,"uid":145837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"咁支共咪唔係人類囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178935aab81b1209aec85f478a9060c7ba4d2d9","tid":2159250,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc